        {
            "title": "美國天然氣期貨飆漲至2022年以來最高水平 寒潮天氣可能影響供應",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 由於寒潮天氣可能推高需求並影響供應，美國<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:天然氣;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/天然氣\">天然氣</a>期貨飆升至2022年以來最高水平，短短三天內漲幅超過70%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">新加坡時間14:31，近月合約上漲13%，至每百萬英熱單位5.506美元。此前兩個交易日累計漲幅已達到50%，交易員爭相將惡劣天氣的影響計入價格。目前，天然氣價格有望創下自1990年有記錄以來的單周漲幅紀錄。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">氣溫下降可能會擾亂美國南部的天然氣生產，所謂的「凍融現象」（即管道內的水凝固）可能會影響供應，而與此同時，預計需求量將上升並將消耗庫存。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-fd42511f-2f23-3c36-83ed-c02bfdfe4bc2-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nkDhpDhsI2ZZajzoG4t6Zw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/no/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/6b07b29e294d4bcf57a51a691a9c0d00\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">價格飆升可能帶動大宗商品更廣泛的上漲行情，會推高美國消費者的成本，而且還會對歐洲和亞洲產生連鎖反應，因為這兩個地區都依賴美國出口海外的液化天然氣供應。這兩個地區的寒潮也在推高天然氣需求。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「天氣仍然是一個關鍵的不確定因素，」The Schneider Capital Group能源分析師Timm Schneider在報告中表示。「我們目前正在密切關注何時才是對交易進行反向操作的最佳時機，因為我們認為目前的價位已經反映了很多市場因素。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">過去幾天，美國氣溫驟降，國家海洋和大氣管理局預測，全美三分之二的地區極有可能出現低於正常水平的氣溫。冬季風暴將於周五至周日逐漸增強，預計天然氣主要產區德克薩斯州將迎來嚴寒天氣。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Natural Gas Hits Highest Since ‘22 as Cold Blast Upends Trade</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Stephen Stapczynski.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%A9%E7%84%B6%E6%B0%A3%E6%9C%9F%E8%B2%A8%E9%A3%86%E6%BC%B2%E8%87%B32022%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A5%E4%BE%86%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3-%E5%AF%92%E6%BD%AE%E5%A4%A9%E6%B0%A3%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89-073523373.html",
